(96, 1, '2018-02-22 23:23:01', '2018-02-22 20:23:01', '<div id=\"pl-57\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-57-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-57-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">ГАРАНТИЯ</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Мы уверены в качестве производимых товаров &#8212; на всю продукцию представляется гарантия.</p>\n</div>\r\n		</div></div><div id=\"pgc-57-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-grid-cell-empty\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ></div><div id=\"pgc-57-0-2\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.33333333333333\" ><div id=\"panel-57-0-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_text panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">КАЧЕСТВО</h3>			<div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Все нашы товары пройшли сертификацию и полностью отвечают европейським и росийським стандартам качества.</p>\n</div>\r\n		</div></div></div><div id=\"pg-57-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-57-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-w